msgid "These settings are available in the **Settings → Telemetry** menu."
msgstr ""

#: src/settings/index.md:284
msgid ""
"\\[!IMPORTANT\\] Changes to these settings only take effect after restarting "
"Cadmus. The application initializes telemetry on startup."
